{"tid":981304,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"廢老彌敦道「玩火」！","createTime":"2019-01-14T08:05:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-14T08:37:38.000Z","uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"e8bb98504cc97a08c0bad4678a432e6348d5e065","tid":981304,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T08:05:07.000Z","msg":"又燒報紙？阿伯彌敦道「玩火」　車輛繞道走<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190114/bkn-20190114154522571-0114_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190114%2Fbkn-20190114154522571-0114_00822_001.html&d=6IUnvXXzGGBLGTx%2Bbciszl0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=8af1aa3e\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190114/bkn-20190114154522571-0114_00822_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/83hJfCX.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F83hJfCX.jpg&h=d01e97a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n早前港鐵旺角站發生縱火案，震驚全城。惟近日在彌敦道，竟有伯伯在馬路疑點燃報紙，再丟向路過車輛？<br />\n<br />\n片段於星期日（13日）晚上近12時被上傳至Facebook群組「Tai Po 大埔」，只見在油麻地彌敦道近中華書局對開位置，有伯伯獨自站在馬路中心，疑似燒報紙。<br />\n<br />\n他頭戴冷帽，左肩披着一塊長度及地的疑似毛巾，又手持燃燒中的疑似報紙。當時不時有車經過，伯伯將「火球」丟開，又踢向馬路中心。<br />\n<br />\n網民紛紛表示震驚︰「依家啲人愈嚟愈X癲」、「旺角地鐵翻版」。有人又指其衣着似「濟公」，或在「表演破地獄」。"},{"pid":"c7d4464886de8328e44367bde95ea6630c795c47","tid":981304,"uid":49812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T08:07:00.000Z","msg":"&hellip;&hellip;"},{"pid":"0c9e9e5fced9ef1aed4b12f8c114c27394e6b71d","tid":981304,"uid":181819,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T08:20:00.000Z","msg":"Good"},{"pid":"afbb0ef7b81f4bfd40bb42ad3c8db7997f8fdc43","tid":981304,"uid":4917,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T08:34:10.000Z","msg":"國之將亡"},{"pid":"58f287fa2e55d3584b737a81d1cc175ce2b19a31","tid":981304,"uid":62011,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-14T08:37:38.000Z","msg":"做乜唔燒死自己啊?"}]}